{"word":"Nahor","slug":"nahor","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nahor</b> - <b>(a)</b> Grandfather of Abraham<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=22'>Gen 11:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=25'>Gen 11:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=26'>1Ch 1:26</a><p/><b>(b)</b> Brother of Abraham<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=27'>Gen 11:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=20'>Gen 22:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=15'>Gen 24:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=53'>Gen 31:53</a><p/><b>NAHUM,</b> the prophet. See Book of Nahum"}]}